(89, 1, '2015-06-28 17:35:45', '2015-06-28 17:35:45', '', 'People', 'We have a very dynamic team structure. Depending on the requirements of the project, we invite a very diverse range of specialists to participate in our work. Furthermore, we usually include a number of students from the Interface Design programme in our projects.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-28 17:35:45', '2015-06-28 17:35:45', '', 9, 'http://jordi.local:8888/fhp/idl/9-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
